  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要为HealthTech设计一个HIPAA合规的数据备份架构。核心需求是：从两个HIPAA Vault数据源开始，经过自动备份和手动操作，最终到达存储层，还要有独立的恢复流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "备份流程",
        "存储",
        "恢复"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了。我注意到您提到了两个Vault作为数据源，但后面又说有自动备份和手动操作两条线。这两个Vault是各自对应不同流程，还是都会参与两种备份方式？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "自动备份",
        "手动操作"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "两个Vault都是数据源，但只有第一个Vault会触发三条分支：一条到EMR_Sync做自动备份，另外两条到LabAnalyzer和第二个EMR_Sync做手动操作。第二个Vault主要是冗余数据源。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，那我先画五个泳道：数据源、自动备份、手动操作、存储、恢复。数据源层放两个HIPAA_Vault节点，命名区分一下，一个叫A一个叫B。自动备份层放EMR_Sync和另一个HIPAA_Vault，手动操作层放LabAnalyzer和EMR_Sync。这样结构清晰吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Источники данных",
        "Автоматические бэкапы",
        "Ручные операции",
        "Хранение",
        "Восстановление"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "泳道划分是对的，但命名上我需要确认：自动备份层里的第二个HIPAA_Vault是做什么的？看起来像是中间缓存？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "Автоматические бэкапы"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，C是EMR_Sync负责同步，D是HIPAA_Vault作为自动备份的临时存储节点，然后D再流向G也就是PatientRecords做长期存储。这是典型的备份-中转-存储三级结构。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "手动操作那条线也需要细化：LabAnalyzer和EMR_Sync都是手动触发，但数据最终要汇总到同一个PatientRecords存储。另外恢复流程要独立出来，从存储层能直接拉起HIPAA_Vault和EMR_Sync。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "Восстановление"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加：手动操作层的E(LabAnalyzer)和F(EMR_Sync)，都从A(Vault)接入。存储层G(PatientRecords)接收D和F的输入，同时G还连接H(LabAnalyzer)。恢复层I(HIPAA_Vault)和J(EMR_Sync)都从G引出。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，H也是LabAnalyzer？存储层为什么需要一个LabAnalyzer？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "Хранение"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "H是存储层内的分析节点，负责对已存储的PatientRecords做离线分析或质检，和手动操作层的E(LabAnalyzer)是不同实例。一个是生产环境的手动分析入口，一个是存储后的数据洞察。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_LabAnalyzer",
        "HealthTech_PatientRecords"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "理解了，就是存储内分析。那整体数据流向再跟我确认一遍：Data → Backup → Storage 这个大方向对吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data",
        "Backup",
        "Storage"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，顶层就是Data -- Backup -- Storage三段式。然后RDS层我们用了五个子图来细化：数据源、自动备份、手动操作、存储、恢复。每个子图内部有具体的HealthTech组件。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data",
        "Backup",
        "Storage",
        "RDS",
        "五个子图"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "恢复流程我还有个补充：I和J都要能从G直接拉起，但J(EMR_Sync)恢复后应该能反向同步回数据源层的Vault吗？还是只读恢复？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "Восстановление",
        "反向同步"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "当前设计是只读恢复，I和J都从G单向引出。如果要支持反向同步，需要加一条J到A或B的回流线。这会改变架构性质，从冷备份变成活同步，合规风险不一样。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "HealthTech_EMR_Sync",
        "HealthTech_HIPAA_Vault",
        "单向恢复",
        "反向同步"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "保持只读恢复，HIPAA要求恢复环境隔离。那当前连接关系再核对：A连C、E、F三条；C连D；D连G；G连H、I、J。对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "D",
        "E",
        "F",
        "G",
        "H",
        "I",
        "J"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完全正确。A→C→D→G是自动备份主线；A→E和A→F是手动操作支线；G→H是存储内分析；G→I和G→J是恢复出口。所有连接都齐了。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "自动备份主线",
        "手动操作支线",
